---
// VisiMisi.astro
---
<section class="py-section-gap px-container-padding-mobile md:px-container-padding-desktop bg-mesh relative" id="tentang">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-section-gap animate-on-scroll animate-fade-up">
      <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg gradient-text mb-4">Visi &amp; Misi</h2>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto font-body-md">Landasan gerak dan arah tujuan Kabinet Karya Adhigana dalam membawa perubahan positif bagi sivitas akademika STMIK Tazkia.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-stretch">
      <!-- Visi Card -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5 glass-panel p-10 rounded-card shadow-soft relative overflow-hidden group hover:-translate-y-4 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 animate-on-scroll animate-fade-up delay-100 cursor-default">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full blur-2xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 group-hover:bg-secondary/30 group-hover:scale-150 transition-all duration-700"></div>
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-container rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 rotate-3 group-hover:rotate-0 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl group-hover:animate-pulse" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">visibility</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-primary mb-6 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300">Visi</h3>
        <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          Mewujudkan BEM STMIK Tazkia sebagai inisiator pergerakan yang progresif, inklusif, dan berdampak nyata bagi sivitas akademika dan masyarakat berbasis data dan keilmuan statistik.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Misi Card -->
      <div class="md:col-span-7 glass-panel p-10 rounded-card shadow-soft relative overflow-hidden group hover:-translate-y-4 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 animate-on-scroll animate-fade-up delay-200 cursor-default">
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-40 h-40 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 group-hover:bg-primary/20 group-hover:scale-150 transition-all duration-700"></div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary-container rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center -rotate-3 group-hover:rotate-0 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-2xl group-hover:animate-pulse" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">format_list_bulleted</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-primary">Misi</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-lowest/50 hover:bg-surface-container-lowest transition-colors">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-1">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm font-bold">check</span>
            </div>
            <p class="font-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Mengoptimalkan pelayanan advokasi mahasiswa yang responsif dan solutif.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-lowest/50 hover:bg-surface-container-lowest transition-colors">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-secondary/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-1">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-sm font-bold">check</span>
            </div>
            <p class="font-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Membangun ruang dialektika intelektual yang kritis dan berbasis data.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-lowest/50 hover:bg-surface-container-lowest transition-colors">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-tertiary/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-1">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary text-sm font-bold">check</span>
            </div>
            <p class="font-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Menyelaraskan pergerakan mahasiswa dengan isu strategis nasional.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
